<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_237" id="118v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_237_r1l1">hanſen Oberngeſeſʒer </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_237_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> hans Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Seicʒen <expan>Sleh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l3">vnd Otten Grefembergers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> wegen das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l4">vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Vnd laſſen euch wiſſen . daʒ <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l5"><expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> cʒu der cʒeit niht anheim ſind . <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> abe </del> ſıe aber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l6"><expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ſie darümb cʒurede ſecʒen / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l7">ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ein antvvurtt wiſſen laſſen . ob die <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l8"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen an vns vordert / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıııj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Om<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> <expan>S<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_237" id="118v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen Oberngeseszer </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Seiczen
                                <expan>Sleh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und Otten Grefembergers,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wegen, das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und lassen euch wissen, daz
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> czu der czeit niht anheim sind.
                                <expan>Wen<ex>n</ex></expan> sie aber
                            <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan>, so <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        sie darümb czu rede seczen und ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ein antwurtt
                        wissen lassen, ob die <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen an uns vordert.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
